metadata.bio:
Kim Jeong-hoon (김정훈; born January 23, 1994), better known by his stage name Coogie (쿠기) is a South Korean rapper signed under AOMG. 

He debuted in 2018 with the single 'HBK' featuring Ted Park under ATMseoul.

He joined Million Market in October 2018.

On December 31, 2021, he left ATMseoul and Million Market and joined Jay Park's AOMG on January 24, 2022.
